{"tid":681780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個朋友在大陸做咗七年嘢，佢咁同我講...","createTime":"2018-05-28T10:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:51:28.000Z","uid":51814,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15bc38401066b70721459b3e242e711539d3dc6a","tid":681780,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"有個朋友在大陸做咗七年嘢，佢咁同我講...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我         <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 而家上面真係唔同哂，發展得好快。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有乜嘢唔同?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 一部手機就可以做好多嘢，手機付費又方便，完全唔駛帶銀包出街。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 香港都用咗八達通成廿年，搭車買嘢都好普及，啟動埋自動增值咪一樣咁用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 上面搭車唔駛截的士㗎，可以叫滴滴近嘅又可以租共享單車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 呢啲都係抄外國科技，但實際上運作成點樣大家都知。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 人人都用㗎喇，你唔用就俾人笑落後。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 乜嘢叫落後先? 遲過人地用就係落後?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁中國遲過其他國家起步，而家終於都追得上人地都算好啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 就算科技追得上，啲人有冇進步先，用嘅人冇公德心咪一樣冇解决到問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 嗯嗯...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你又知唔知呢幾年香港都唔同哂?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有乜嘢唔同?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 以前政府做得唔好市民可以出嚟集會遊行表示不滿，而家郁啲就話你搞港獨分裂國家拉你坐監，仲邊有人夠膽出嚟行吖?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁佔中嗰班人係幾麻煩嘅，政府都話同佢地談判咪唔好阻街囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 政府談判完一步都唔讓，連開放返公民廣場俾示威者用都唔肯，咁有冇誠意傾先?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁都可以用啲和平手法嚟同政府傾嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你話要和平喇，就去參選立法會議員啦，入議會用正路維護公義啦，又無端端俾個選舉主任話唔夠真誠取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 嗰個係旺角暴動主謀，係要小心啲嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁好啦當你贏，然後又點呢?政府以宣誓無效為理由，先後DQ咗梁游羅姚等6名已當選嘅非建制派議員，你選咗佢入去都要踢返出嚟，政府究竟有冇誠意聽市民意見呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁都唔可以亂咁鬧中國係支那嘅，你就算唔愛國都要尊重吓國家嘅法律嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 講尊重法律?大白象高鐵仲用一地兩檢方式破壞基本法，咁有冇尊重吓香港嘅法律呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 起條高鐵都係方便我呢啲要上去做嘢嘅香港人啫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 喂你住元朗真心講會唔會去坐高鐵呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哎吔，你唔好成個連登仔咁成日盲反中國啦，香港有冇呢啲正嘢先。<br />\n<br />\n朋友隨即打開手機内各地大波長腿美女圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你留喺香港食到呢啲女，先同我講贏啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你啱，港女嘅質素真係冇得比，香港應該要引入每日150個呢啲女，如果唔係香港人遲早絕種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 嗯嗯..."},{"pid":"d06b4d5dbc3e84136cbb40b9e6171ef28bb5566e","tid":681780,"uid":133754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"b575d313b03f592f7b5f18090cb07929182cb5a7","tid":681780,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"TLDR"},{"pid":"ae7d32631c2b91ff978675e94e99d57e61a03642","tid":681780,"uid":124279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e656cb83c52e4172adeb3b94250acddee6883af6","tid":681780,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"典型大陸思維"},{"pid":"97edd79a599b2c1273e03748564ccae19d61fb15","tid":681780,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"蝗化"},{"pid":"6b1adc065d13e65e26ad9c909994d7f9bf224cee","tid":681780,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"中港矛盾一講到港女就真係駁唔到"}]}